    },
    {
      "id": "Oo9CtFfAGzLbrritVcyK3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 322,
      "y": 365,
      "width": 818.4395141601562,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 196041759,
      "version": 167,
      "versionNonce": 830622943,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780714716194,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Without Agent Evaluations, the Agents can put us into the risk as it is invloved in \nvarious domains like healthcare,banking,law,infrastrucutre etc.\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Without Agent Evaluations, the Agents can put us into the risk as it is invloved in \nvarious domains like healthcare,banking,law,infrastrucutre etc.\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jWQy9mn8H7gH7DQroEtSa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 311,
      "y": 473,
      "width": 566.0396118164062,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2060608831,
      "version": 477,
      "versionNonce": 359637375,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780714899869,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Business & Operational risk:\n1. Wrong Decisions can endup in financial loss\n2. Agent Failure will damage the brand or reputation\n3. We may end up with Regulatory and legal penalities\n4. It may lead to cascading failure\n\nEthical & Social Risk:\n1. There can be biased and discrimination in the Outcomes\n    2. Privacy violation in the Agents\n3. Spreading misinformation\n4. providing inappropiate responses to harm the users\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Business & Operational risk:\n1. Wrong Decisions can endup in financial loss\n2. Agent Failure will damage the brand or reputation\n3. We may end up with Regulatory and legal penalities\n4. It may lead to cascading failure\n\nEthical & Social Risk:\n1. There can be biased and discrimination in the Outcomes\n    2. Privacy violation in the Agents\n3. Spreading misinformation\n4. providing inappropiate responses to harm the users\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tgquKOE8DyeQDrUjSUdmc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 351,
      "y": 841,
      "width": 1149.479248046875,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 863704671,
      "version": 944,
      "versionNonce": 655757617,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780715547078,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Real-world Failures:\n\n\n1. Halluncinations - Agents needs to invest in facts with high accuracy - Medical/Legal chatbots\n2.  Inconsistency - Agents needs to be very reliable - Customer Support, Compliance\n3. Context Limits - Relevant context are passed to the agents , if we need we can add sub-agents to avoid this.\n4. Reasoning Failures - mathematical , logical issues that fails to make the proper decision due to wrong observations\n5. Bias & Fairness - Ensure your application is not discrimatory based on demographics/gender\n6. Jailbreaking - Safety Gaurdrails\n7.Tool User Error - Enforce Tool SCHEMA and TOOL REGISTERY\n8. Poor Calibration - Trust - Over confidence\n9. Cost & Latency - cost to be lower and users need to have the faster responses10\n10. Prompt Injection - Wrong instruction to override the prompt\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Real-world Failures:\n\n\n1. Halluncinations - Agents needs to invest in facts with high accuracy - Medical/Legal chatbots\n2.  Inconsistency - Agents needs to be very reliable - Customer Support, Compliance\n3. Context Limits - Relevant context are passed to the agents , if we need we can add sub-agents to avoid this.\n4. Reasoning Failures - mathematical , logical issues that fails to make the proper decision due to wrong observations\n5. Bias & Fairness - Ensure your application is not discrimatory based on demographics/gender\n6. Jailbreaking - Safety Gaurdrails\n7.Tool User Error - Enforce Tool SCHEMA and TOOL REGISTERY\n8. Poor Calibration - Trust - Over confidence\n9. Cost & Latency - cost to be lower and users need to have the faster responses10\n10. Prompt Injection - Wrong instruction to override the prompt\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
