      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "EU AI ACT:\n\n\n-> Each AI models classfies what domain it serves and list out the damage it can cause on that particular field\n-> What are the obligation has been handled carefully to migitate the risk",
      "autoResize": true,
